  "text": "HCR rats displayed increased aerobic function and decreased fat mass consistent with prior characterization of the strain, whereas LCR rats displayed decreased aerobic function and increased fat mass [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Female LCR and HCR rats were not different in their overall weights. Prior studies have shown clear differences in body weight in female rats, though less pronounced compared to their male counterparts [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
